'''阿科博'''是[[南蘇丹|南蘇丹]]東北部的小鎮，位於首都[[朱巴|朱巴]]東北約450公里的[[瓊萊省|瓊萊省]]<ref>[http://distancecalculator.globefeed.com/Sudan_Distance_Result.asp?fromplace=Juba%20()%20(Airport)%20&toplace=Nahr%20Akubu%20()&fromlat=4.872006&tolat=7.7833333&fromlng=31.601117&tolng=33.05 Map Showing Juba And Akobo With Distance Marker]</ref>，毗鄰[[埃塞俄比亞|埃塞俄比亞]]，鎮上有機場設施，2011年7月居民人數約1,000<ref>[http://www.collinsmaps.com/maps/Sudan/Jonglei/Akobo/P484762.00.aspx Estimated Population of Akobo In 2011] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111008220841/http://www.collinsmaps.com/maps/Sudan/Jonglei/Akobo/P484762.00.aspx |date=2011-10-08 }}</ref>。阿科博有185名婦女和小孩在2009年8月的屠殺中遇害<ref>Peter Martell, [http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8194060.stm "Horrors of South Sudan massacre"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/world/africa/8194060.stm |date=20190713153407 }}, BBC News, 10 August 2009</ref>。

